{"data":[{"date":"13:41 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Fulham vs Crystal Palace 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (Premier League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-fulham-vs-crystal-palace-21h00-ngay-118-premier-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fulham vs Crystal Palace l\u00fac 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i Premier League Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh NHA 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Fulham vs Crystal Palace 21h00 ng\u00e0y 118 Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Fulham vs Crystal Palace 21h00 ng\u00e0y 118 Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Fulham-vs-Crystal-Palace.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Fulham vs Crystal Palace</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>Fulham vs Crystal Palace: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Sau 4 m\u00f9a ch\u01a1i \u1edf Championship, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Fulham c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng cao nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 Premier League. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Craven Cottage v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 khung \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra th\u00ec Fulham c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Schurrle (t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea) t\u1eeb Dortmund hay Vietto t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid, Chambers t\u1eeb Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean ph\u00eda Crystal Palace, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 n\u00e0o m\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jordan Ayew, Meyer. D\u1eabu v\u1eady th\u00ec s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, d\u00f9 m\u1edbi th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0ng Fulham t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m Crystal Palace.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9, Crystal Palace th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua: th\u1eafng 4/5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Fulham ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2/8 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cho s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a 1 CLB b\u1edfi c\u00e1c HLV th\u01b0\u1eddng \u01b0u ti\u00ean th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m t\u00e2n binh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Fulham ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 e ng\u1ea1i Crystal Palace \u1edf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Craven Cottage. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y Fulham c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a trong 4 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTin r\u1eb1ng Fulham s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 quan trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n2 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 43 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Fulham th\u1eafng 17 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n Crystal Palace th\u1eafng 11 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\nFulham: Mawson, Tim Ream v\u00e0 Ayite ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f2n Denis Odoi b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2.<br>\r\nCrystal Palace: Scott Dann ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Meyer c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2251","checkdouble":"194255"},{"date":"14:54 11/08","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, Pogba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-len-tieng-khi-pogba-va-sanchez-tranh-nhau-penalty.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa MU v\u00e0 Leicester v\u1eeba qua. V\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, Pogba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, Pogba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/mourinho-len-tieng-khi-pogba-va-sanchez-tranh-nhau-penalty.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao sau khi gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/paul-pogba-44584.html\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Pogba</span> cho th\u1ea5y anh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Premier League v\u1edbi Leicester v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 2 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u00f9 Schmeichel \u0111\u00e3 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, Man United ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00f9i l\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 83, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi Luke Shaw ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Vardy g\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n cho Leicester ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cb\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb th\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi Man United. B\u1edfi m\u1ed7i khi anh l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League. V\u00e0 Man United \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong c\u1ea3 11 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Pogba ngang b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ryan Babel c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan c\u0169ng gi\u00fap The Kop gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong 11 tr\u1eadn m\u00e0 anh ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man United t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 Premier League v\u00e0 Champions League. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean th\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester-172-194247.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-leicester-tran-dau-vong-1-premier-league-201819-372-194203.html\">MU 2-1 Leicester: M\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00fdt ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2250","checkdouble":"194256"},{"date":"15:03 11/08","title":"Emery quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng m\u1ea1ch thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Guardiola","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/emery-quyet-tam-chan-dung-mach-thua-truoc-guardiola.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau khi hai ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tranh nhau qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Paul Pogba cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ecbn v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh anh m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0 gi\u1edd ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cho Man Utd.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i, Alexis Sanchez c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi b\u1ecb tranh gi\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi anh r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi su\u00f4n s\u1ebb sau n\u1eeda n\u0103m kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 \u1edf Old Trafford. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i sao Chile \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u00f3 khi s\u00fat b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang tay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Leicester trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/mourinho-len-tieng-khi-pogba-va-sanchez-tranh-nhau-penalty.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh \u0111\u00e1 penalty \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec gi\u1eefa anh v\u00e0 Sanchez. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus c\u00f3 n\u00f3i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh ri\u00eang m\u1ed9t ai \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch s\u00fat penalty c\u1ea3, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 HLV c\u0169ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp v\u1edbi nhau ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n can thi\u1ec7p. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u01b0\u1eddng cho Alexis v\u00ec n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Man Utd m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ti\u1ebfp l\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh, HLV Jose Mourinho c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19: \u201cPaul s\u00fat penalty r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 hai v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ba \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p thi\u1ebfu t\u1ef1 tin v\u00ec m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean Paul gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea5m 11m. Sau c\u00f9ng th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2018 c\u01a1 m\u00e0. Nh\u00ecn m\u00e0 xem, Kasper Schmeichel b\u1eaft ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ra sao v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2249","checkdouble":"194257"},{"date":"15:22 11/08","title":"Klopp ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi khi Kepa ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Alisson","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/klopp-phan-khoi-khi-kepa-pha-ky-luc-cua-alisson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u00e2n binh gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u0169 b\u1ecf \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda \u1edf Anh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, khi Kepa Arrizabalanga v\u00e0 Alisson Becker ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t Premier League. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng, k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong khung g\u1ed7 \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb Liverpool v\u00e0 Chelsea ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1, t\u1eeb 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00ean 72 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp vui Kepa ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp vui Kepa ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/klopp-phan-khoi-khi-kepa-pha-ky-luc-cua-alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kepa ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Alisson ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi HLV Jurgen Klopp, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin m\u1eebng cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1edf Anfield. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec3n Brazil gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u0169 b\u1ecf \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 t\u1eeb c\u00e1i m\u00e1c \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Kepa v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y di\u1ec5n ra theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho Alisson, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u1edfi ch\u00fang ta lu\u00f4n cho r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3, Alisson v\u00e0 Kepa kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Klopp nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u00eam v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i: \u201cChelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1edfi th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Bilbao l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3, ho\u1eb7c anh tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1n ho\u1eb7c m\u1eddi anh \u0111i cho. D\u00f9 sao, th\u1eddi th\u1ebf c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi ch\u1ec9 \u00edt n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y th\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng ai ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua v\u1edbi c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 cao \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00f2ng 1 m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2017/18, Liverpool ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Anfield trong khi Chelsea ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Alisson m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f2n Kepa s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n sau.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet-172-194190.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet-172-194190.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb m\u00f9a chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018: B\u1ed1n th\u1eadp ni\u00ean b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f3a m\u1ed9t t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u1ecb bi\u1ec7t</span><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. Ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n Alisson v\u00e0 Kepa c\u0169ng l\u00e0 hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2248","checkdouble":"194258"},{"date":"14:39 11/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Newcastle vs Tottenham 18h30 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (Premier League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/newcastle-vs-tottenham-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Newcastle vs Tottenham: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Newcastle vs Tottenham gi\u1ea3i Premier League Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh NHA 2018/19 l\u00fac 18h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 11/8.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Newcastle vs Tottenham: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Newcastle vs Tottenham gi\u1ea3i Premier League Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh NHA 2018/19 l\u00fac 18h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 11/8.</h2></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2247","checkdouble":"194259"},{"date":"15:41 11/08","title":"Mourinho l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khi Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh nhau penalty","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-len-tieng-khi-pogba-va-sanchez-tranh-nhau-penalty.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau khi hai ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tranh nhau qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Paul Pogba cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ecbn v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh anh m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0 gi\u1edd ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cho Man Utd.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i, Alexis Sanchez c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi b\u1ecb tranh gi\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi anh r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi su\u00f4n s\u1ebb sau n\u1eeda n\u0103m kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 \u1edf Old Trafford. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i sao Chile \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u00f3 khi s\u00fat b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang tay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Leicester trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/mourinho-len-tieng-khi-pogba-va-sanchez-tranh-nhau-penalty.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh \u0111\u00e1 penalty \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec gi\u1eefa anh v\u00e0 Sanchez. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus c\u00f3 n\u00f3i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh ri\u00eang m\u1ed9t ai \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch s\u00fat penalty c\u1ea3, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 HLV c\u0169ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp v\u1edbi nhau ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n can thi\u1ec7p. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u01b0\u1eddng cho Alexis v\u00ec n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Man Utd m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ti\u1ebfp l\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh, HLV Jose Mourinho c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19: \u201cPaul s\u00fat penalty r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 hai v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ba \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p thi\u1ebfu t\u1ef1 tin v\u00ec m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean Paul gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea5m 11m. Sau c\u00f9ng th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2018 c\u01a1 m\u00e0. Nh\u00ecn m\u00e0 xem, Kasper Schmeichel b\u1eaft ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ra sao v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2246","checkdouble":"194260"},{"date":"15:38 11/08","title":"Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e2n binh MU sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Leicester","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/pogba-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-fred-sau-tran-thang-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Pogba \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn v\u00e0o t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Man United.</h2><h2>Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Fred</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt ng\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng Pogba \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester \u0111\u00eam qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPogba kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m penalty ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Luke Shaw ph\u00fat 83 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh v\u00e0 Fred c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u1eefa anh v\u00e0 Fred.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Fred sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Fred sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/pogba-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-fred-sau-tran-thang-leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Fred sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y Fred l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Pereira d\u00f9 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng th\u00fa th\u1eadt l\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi c\u00f3 Fred c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m vui h\u01a1n khi c\u00f3 Fred trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Pogba ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c tranh c\u00e3i v\u1edbi Sanchez</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n penalty. Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1 penalty nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb Pogba t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y: <em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e3nh tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1 penalty. M\u00e0 d\u00f9 HLV c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng cho nhau. H\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n penalty. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00f3 cho Sanchez. \u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVideo t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester:<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester-172-194247.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-21-cua-mu-truoc-leicester-172-194222.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2245","checkdouble":"194261"},{"date":"16:02 11/08","title":"HLV Sarri k\u00eau g\u1ecdi C\u0110V Chelsea ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/hlv-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Chelsea. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. \u00d4ng c\u00f9ng Chelsea thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c, kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Community Shield c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 59 tu\u1ed5i thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp cho The Blues \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7, Sarri m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV Chelsea sau khi h\u1ecd sa th\u1ea3i Antonio Conte. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng cho m\u00f9a m\u1edbi b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea s\u1eafp t\u1edbi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi Conte v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m quen.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/hlv-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sarri l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Sarri c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Chelsea. \u00d4ng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng CLB. Sarri c\u0169ng l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho m\u00ecnh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb C\u0110V v\u00e0 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft r\u1ea5t r\u00f5\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng trong n\u1eeda sau c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1. T\u00f4i d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-21h00-ngay-118-nhay-mua-cung-sarriball-172-194230.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-21h00-ngay-118-nhay-mua-cung-sarriball.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-21h00-ngay-118-nhay-mua-cung-sarriball-172-194230.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea (21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8): Nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa c\u00f9ng Sarriball</span><br>\r\n<span>Tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Conte \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Sarri. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2017/18.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec9nh ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng (\u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 5 Premier League). V\u00ec v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u1edf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec9nh ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh trong 1 ho\u1eb7c 2 th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cL\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n ch\u1edd th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mang l\u1ea1i. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-cau-thu-sap-roi-chelsea-172-194238.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/aubameyang-172-194218.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-chelsea-len-tieng-xac-nhan-tuong-lai-cua-hazard-172-194216.html\">HLV Chelsea l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-ung-ho-chelsea-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-the-gioi-vi-thu-mon-kepa-172-194215.html\">Pep Guardiola \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Chelsea vung ti\u1ec1n v\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ai-o-real-madrid-da-khuyen-kovacic-ra-di-cap-ben-chelsea-172-194208.html\">Ai \u1edf Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 khuy\u00ean Kovacic ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2244","checkdouble":"194262"},{"date":"16:29 11/08","title":"HLV Leicester: \u201cTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/hlv-claude-puel-phat-bieu-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U th\u1eafng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt Leicester</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. H\u1ecd m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 do c\u00f4ng Paul Pogba t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Leicester l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m. Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David De Gea m\u1edbi gi\u00fap M.U tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. \u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 83, Luke Shaw nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t, khi\u1ebfn b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 ph\u00fat 90+2 c\u1ee7a Jamie Vardy kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Claude-Puel-phat-bieu-sau-tran-MU-2-1-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Puel b\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Vardy kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Claude Puel h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U, n\u01a1i c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh James Maddison, Ricardo Pereira v\u00e0 Rachid Ghezzal c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ra m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c\u201d, Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester. \u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 sau v\u00e0i ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa ngay.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Puel cua Leicester\" title=\"HLV Puel cua Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/hlv-claude-puel-phat-bieu-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong hi\u1ec7p 1, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ta nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, sau khi th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ebd tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sang h\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u00e1c. Sau c\u00f9ng, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPuel ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: \u201c\u0110\u00f4i khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0y d\u00f9 s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-tran-mu-21-leicester-bong-dang-sieu-doi-truong-xuat-hien-172-194228.html\">M.U 2-1 Leicester: B\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng \u201cSi\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester-172-194247.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\">Mourinho g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: \u201cPogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i th\u00fa\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/danh-bai-leicester-mourinho-ca-ngoi-suc-manh-tap-the-cua-mu-172-194223.html\">\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester, Mourinho ca ng\u1ee3i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-21-cua-mu-truoc-leicester-172-194222.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2243","checkdouble":"194263"},{"date":"17:29 11/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Huddersfield vs Chelsea 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (Premier League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Huddersfield vs Chelsea: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea gi\u1ea3i Premier League Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh NHA 2018/19 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 11/8.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Huddersfield vs Chelsea: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea gi\u1ea3i Premier League Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh NHA 2018/19 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 11/8.</h2></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2242","checkdouble":"194264"},{"date":"09:56 11/08","title":"Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn ra th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/unai-emery-da-chon-ra-thu-mon-bat-chinh-truoc-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Unai Emery s\u1ebd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City, v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cech b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh m\u1eafc 6 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 36 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Arsenal ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 48 b\u00e0n thua \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/unai-emery-da-chon-ra-thu-mon-bat-chinh-truoc-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Cech s\u1ebd b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City thay v\u00ec Leno</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal-172-190840.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua Leno</span>, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Petr Cech \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. HLV Emery \u0111ang \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u trong vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo The Telegraph, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Unai Emery s\u1ebd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City, v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 36 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Cech thay v\u00ec t\u00e2n binh Leno. C\u0169ng theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb The Telegraph, c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Man xanh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Emery ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Arsenal m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Per Mertesacker l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Arsenal, song anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Laurent Koscielny \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/4-van-de-hlv-emery-can-giai-quyet-truoc-mua-giai-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Unai Emery n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Mertesacker \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Arsenal c\u00f2n Koscielny ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 10 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, HLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u sao PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKoscielny, Petr Cech, Aaron Ramsey, Granit Xhaka v\u00e0 Mesut Ozil l\u00e0 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2241","checkdouble":"194239"},{"date":"10:19 11/08","title":"HLV Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Real?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-sau-khi-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge t\u1edbi Bernabeu c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed phong \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Petr Cech ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-sau-khi-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Thibaut Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Courtois l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn anh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bernabeu thi \u0111\u1ea5u, anh mu\u1ed1n g\u1ea7n g\u0169i c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Courtois \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real, The Blues thu v\u1ec1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-194131.html\" target=\"_blank\">Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span>, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Bernabeu kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n. L\u00fd do l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i t\u1edbi Los Blancos l\u00e0 v\u00ec gia \u0111\u00ecnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf g\u1ea7n c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1ee7a Courtois?</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge t\u1edbi Bernabeu c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri\" title=\"Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nhan-dinh-Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-vong-1-Premier-League-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 l\u1eafm. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Real Madrid. D\u00f9 sao c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Chelsea, t\u00f4i ch\u00fac c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi Eden Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Chelsea. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn 4 l\u1ea7n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi Kepa c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Courtois hay kh\u00f4ng, HLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 23 tu\u1ed5i m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Kepa s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng do Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Mateo Kovacic \u00f4ng chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u1edbi Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2240","checkdouble":"194240"},{"date":"09:13 11/08","title":"Klopp v\u1eabn cay c\u00fa v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ramos l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/klopp-van-cay-cu-va-khang-dinh-ramos-la-noi-si-nhuc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t hay kh\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fenerbahce h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Origi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-southampton-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tien-dao-cua-liverpool-172-194142.html\" target=\"_blank\">Danny Ings t\u1edbi Southampton</span> theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i, song c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Divock Origi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/26/Fenerbahce-muon-dua-Divock-Origi-roi-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Divock Origi mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Firmino, Sturridge v\u00e0 Solanke, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1995 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Origi, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Watford, Crystal Palace hay Wolves, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Liverpool y\u00eau c\u1ea7u khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t hay kh\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Origi t\u1edbi Fenerbahce l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n HLV Klopp c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Origi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Fenerbahce c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 Liverpool v\u00e0 Origi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Origi\" title=\"Origi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/29/sao-xit-liverpool-doi-lenh-klopp-de-ra-di.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Origi s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Origi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec The Kop c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTTCN H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua, song nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Origi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, Liverpool s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Klopp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2239","checkdouble":"194241"},{"date":"09:12 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Stoke vs Brentford 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-stoke-vs-brentford-21h00-ngay-118-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Stoke vs Brentford l\u00fac 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Stoke vs Brentford 21h ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Stoke vs Brentford 21h ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Stoke-vs-Brentford.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Stoke vs Brentford</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>Stoke vs Brentford: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Stoke \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i, khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh. Trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a H\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365 c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Shaqiri, Ramadan Sobhi, Marc Muniesa hay Lee Grant. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i HLV Gary Rowett c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng thay th\u1ebf nh\u01b0 Oghenekaro Etebo, Adam Federici, James McClean, Tom Ince hay Sam Clucas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGiai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u00f9a H\u00e8, Stoke r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 6 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1edbi Walsall. \u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19, h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tan n\u00e1t 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Leeds United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 2, Stoke c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Brendford, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1eebng 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. \u1ede 2 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u00f3, Stoke \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1eeda tr\u00ean b\u1edfi l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i \u1edf Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBrenford \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 5-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e2n binh Rotherham United, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, b\u1edfi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2238","checkdouble":"194242"},{"date":"11:01 11/08","title":"HLV Emery khi\u1ebfn NHM Arsenal bu\u1ed3n vui l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/hlv-emery-khien-nhm-arsenal-buon-vui-lan-lon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e1o tin vui t\u1eeb Ramsey song kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Emery ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Arsenal s\u1eafp gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ramsey</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aaron Ramsey v\u1edbi Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aaron Ramsey\" title=\"Aaron Ramsey\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Unai-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Aaron Ramsey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chi-40-trieu-bang-chelsea-quyet-tam-mua-bang-duoc-sao-khung-arsenal-172-193778.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ramsey</span>, Real v\u00e0 Barca c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e1o tin vui t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i: &ldquo;Vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Arsenal<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ramsey, HLV Unai Emery c\u00f2n ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ospina bat chinh truoc Atletico Madrid\" title=\"Ospina b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/Unai-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ospina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Carl Jenkinson, David Ospina v\u00e0 Joel Campbell c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. C\u00f2n vi\u1ec7c ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n hay b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a BL\u0110&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Emery c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Emile Smith Rowe v\u00e0 Eddie Nketiah s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Man City trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2237","checkdouble":"194244"}]}